Egypt’s Cabinet Approves Raising Monopoly Fine to $50.2 Million

-- B y   A b d e l   L a t i f   W a h b a
-- 
2011-09-25T16:41:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/egypt-s-cabinet-approves-raising-monopoly-fine-to-50-2-million.html
Egypt ’s cabinet approved amending
the anti-monopoly law to increase the fine for violations to at
least 300 million Egyptian pounds ($50.2 million) from 50
million pounds previously, Cabinet spokesman Mohamed Hegazy told
reporters in Cairo today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
